message.content:
Enhancements to Business Intelligence Tools and Reports

Tools

1. **Data Visualization**: We will be upgrading our data visualization tool to include more advanced features such as interactive dashboards and real-time data updates. 2. **Reporting**: Our reporting tool will now include more customizable options for users, including the ability to create personalized dashboards and reports.

Reports

1. **Sales Performance Report**: This report will now include additional metrics such as customer segmentation and product performance analysis. 2. **Marketing Analytics Report**: This report will now include more detailed information on campaign performance and customer engagement.

Metadata Enhancements

1. **Data Governance**: We will be implementing a data governance framework to ensure data quality and consistency across all reports and tools. 2. **Data Discovery**: Our data discovery tool will now include more advanced features such as data profiling and data lineage analysis.
